userStories.description:
In main.rs, after EnterAlternateScreen (line 146) and Clear(ClearType::All) (line 147), add Clear(ClearType::Purge) to clear the entire scrollback buffer. ClearType::All only clears the visible screen; ClearType::Purge clears the entire scrollback buffer so users cannot scroll up past the TUI.

Key file: crates/baro-tui/src/main.rs lines 146-147

Change line 147 from:
  execute!(tty, Clear(ClearType::All))?;
To:
  execute!(tty, Clear(ClearType::All))?;
  execute!(tty, Clear(ClearType::Purge))?;

Also verify the import of ClearType includes Purge (it's part of crossterm::terminal::ClearType enum, no new import needed).
